}\n\n'''Yuanshan Township''' ({{zh|c=\u54e1\u5c71\u9109|p=Yu\u00e1nsh\u0101n Xi\u0101ng}}) is a [[Township (Taiwan)|rural township]] in the western part of [[Yilan County, Taiwan|Yilan County]], [[Taiwan]].\n\n==Geography==\n* Area: {{convert|111.91|km2|abbr=on}}\n* Population: 32,377 (2014)\n\n==Administrative divisions==\nThe township comprises 16 villages:<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yuanshan.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=AFE7E366B74D9837|script-title=zh:\u9109\u6c11\u4ee3\u8868\u6703|language=zh-tw|accessdate=27 November 2019|website=\u5713\u5c71\u9109\u516c\u6240 Yuanshan Township Office|quote=[\u7b2c\u4e00\u9078\u5340\uff3f\u54e1\u5c71\u6751\u3001\u60e0\u597d\u6751\u3001\u5c1a\u5fb7\u6751][\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9078\u5340\uff3f\u4e03\u8ce2\u6751\u3001\u6df1\u6e9d\u6751\u3001\u84c1\u5df7\u6751\u3001\u5167\u57ce\u6751\u3001\u4e2d\u83ef\u6751][\u7b2c\u4e09\u9078\u5340\uff3f\u6c38\u548c\u6751\u3001\u982d\u5206\u6751\u3001\u6795\u5c71\u6751\u3001\u540c\u6a02\u6751][\u7b2c\u56db\u9078\u5340\uff3f\u6e56\u6771\u6751\u3001\u6e56\u5317\u6751\u3001\u6e56\u897f\u6751\u3001\u9038\u4ed9\u6751]}}</ref>\n* Hubei (\u6e56\u5317\u6751), Huihao (\u60e0\u597d\u6751), Hudong/Hutung (\u6e56\u6771\u6751), Huxi (\u6e56\u897f\u6751), Neicheng (\u5167\u57ce\u6751), Qixian (\u4e03\u8ce2\u6751), Shangde (\u5c1a\u5fb7\u6751), Shengou (\u6df1\u6e9d\u6751), Tongle (\u540c\u6a02\u6751), Toufen (\u982d\u5206\u6751), Yixian (\u9038\u4ed9\u6751), Yonghe (\u6c38\u548c\u6751), Yuanshan (\u54e1\u5c71\u6751), Zhenshan (\u6795\u5c71\u6751), Zhenxiang (\u84c1\u5df7\u6751) and Zhonghua (\u4e2d\u83ef\u6751).\n\n==Tourist attractions==\n* [[Fushan Botanical Garden]]\n* [[Jim and Dad's Brewery]]\n* [[Kavalan Distillery]]\n* [[Yuanshan Park]]\n\n==Transportation==\nThe nearest train station to the township is [[Yilan Station]] of the [[Taiwan Railway Administration]], located in [[Yilan City]].\n*Highway\n**[[File:TW PHW7.svg|23px|\u7701\u9053]][[Provincial Highway 7 (Taiwan)|Provincial Highway 7]]:Northern Cross-Country Highway\n***[[File:TW PHW7d.svg|23px|\u7701\u9053]][[Provincial Highway 7 (Taiwan)|Prov 7d]]\n*Bus\n**List of bus routes in Yilan\n***Kamalan Bus Inc.\n****'''<span style=\"color:red;\">751</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Baomin Temple\n****'''<span style=\"color:red;\">752</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Taipei Veterans General Hospital Yuanshan Branch\n****'''<span style=\"color:red;\">753</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Shuanglian Pond\n****'''<span style=\"color:red;\">755</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Wanglongpo\n***[[Kuo-Kuang Motor Transportation]]\n****'''<span style=\"color:green;\">G12</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Songluo\n****'''<span style=\"color:green;\">G15</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Da Jiao Xi\n****'''<span style=\"color:red;\">1785</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Waiyuanshan - Zuntou\n****'''<span style=\"color:red;\">1786</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Shengou - Neicheng\n****'''<span style=\"color:red;\">1789</span>''' Yilan Transfer Station - Zhensha - Dajiaoxi\n\n==Notable natives==\n* [[Yang Li-hua]], opera performer\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Yuanshan Township, Yilan County}}\n* [http://www.yuanshan.gov.tw/ Yuanshan Township Office] {{in lang|zh}}\n* [http://www2.ysvh.gov.tw/english/ Yuanshan Veterans Hospital]\n\n{{Taiwan Yilan divisions}}\n{{Townships in Taiwan}}\n\n[[Category:Townships in Yilan County, Taiwan]]\n\n\n{{taiwan-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Coord|24.744337|N|121.66838|E|display=title}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n | official_name            = Yuanshan Township<br>\u54e1\u5c71\u9109\n | nickname                 = \n | motto                    = \n | settlement_type          = [[Township (Taiwan)|Rural township]]\n | image_skyline            = \u3010\u5b9c\u862d\u666f\u9ede\u3011\u5409\u59c6\u8001\u7239\u5564\u9152\u5de5\u5ee0 (30386873005).jpg\n | image_flag               = \